            </section-body>
         </informative-references></references></definition-item>
<definition-item><classification-symbol scheme="cpc">F42C7/00</classification-symbol><definition-title>Fuzes actuated by application of a predetermined mechanical force, e.g. tension, torsion, pressure  (by ammunition impact <class-ref scheme="cpc">F42C1/00</class-ref>, by exposure to a predetermined ambient fluid pressure <class-ref scheme="cpc">F42C5/00</class-ref>)</definition-title><definition-statement>
