         <section-body>
            <paragraph-text type="preamble">This place covers:</paragraph-text>
            <paragraph-text type="body">The fuse is actuated by application of a mechanical force, i.e. the forceful relative displacement of two components of the fuze relative to each other. Basically a mechanical switch triggering a detonation.</paragraph-text>
